## Installation

1. Extract to `/var/lib/grafana/plugins/kmluvce-aiassistant-app/`
2. Add to grafana.ini:
   ```
   [plugins]
   allow_loading_unsigned_plugins = kmluvce-aiassistant-app
   ```
3. Restart Grafana
4. Enable in Configuration â†’ Plugins

## Usage

1. Click ğŸ¤– button (bottom-right)
2. Configure MCP server URL in settings
3. Ask questions!

